title: Dragon Ball Le (Doujinshi)
description:
Description :
        It's been 10 years since Goku, Shenron and The Dragon Balls disappeared. But the bad guys in hell still didn't give up their intention to destroy the Earth, so they silently created a monster named "Zero" and the creators of this monster are Dr. Gero, Dr. Myu, The Magician Babidi and Dr. RaichiDragon Ball LE has no affiliation with Akira Toriyama, Funamation, Toei Animation, or Fuji TV. Dragon Ball LE is a fan-made doujinshi created by Doramani and is made purely for entertainment.
